### Sikeres regisztráció
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "david",
  "email": "david@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Hibás validáció - üres username
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "",
  "email": "david@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Hibás validáció - rövid jelszó
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "short"
}

### Hibás validáció - érvénytelen email
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Conflict - duplikált username
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "david",
  "email": "different@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Conflict - duplikált email
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "different_user",
  "email": "david@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Sikeres login
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "david",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Hibás login - rossz jelszó
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "david",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### Hibás login - nem létező user
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nonexistent",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Validáció - üres username
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Current user - token nélkül
GET http://localhost:8080/users/me

### Current user - tokennel
# @name loginRequest
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "david",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {% client.global.set("authToken", response.body.token); %}

### Current user - használva a mentett tokent
GET http://localhost:8080/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}